Author: soclosetoit
Text: Ugh I feel you. “Normal” dieting and losing weight  somehow feels just as bad, maybe even worse than bingeing and gaining 5 pounds. Just remember that, just like you said, our brains and thoughts can lie to us, like really easily, so it’s good to notice thoughts and feelings with skepticism and not just accept them as true. Good luck on your finals and with everything!

Author: orthofuckyrself
Text: I feel you. I've been eating maintenance and then also had a cheat meal... and I feel like I'm fucking huge even though I know that's absurd.   We're gonna do this- we're gonna get through finals and the holidays. We got this :p
